explanations.description: The prefix "hom-" appears in various words, often related to concepts of sameness, similarity, or identity, such as "homogeneous", "homology", "homophobic", "homosexuality", and "homestead". Additionally, words with the prefix "homo-" are also present, such as "homicide". Other words like "homage" and "homers" (as in a home run in baseball) also appear.
